properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Chincoteague to Parramore Island VA out 20 nm
properties.headline: Low Water Advisory issued February 9 at 10:24AM EST until February 9 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Wakefield VA
properties.description:
* WHAT...For the Low Water Advisory, abnormally low water levels
expected. For the Small Craft Advisory, southwest winds 15 to
20 kt with gusts up to 25 kt and seas 3 to 5 ft expected.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Chincoteague to Parramore Island
VA out 20 nm.

* WHEN...For the Low Water Advisory, until 4 PM EST this
afternoon. For the Small Craft Advisory, from 6 AM to 2 PM EST
Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft. Below
normal water levels will result in hazardous navigating
conditions.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

Mariners should navigate shallow waters with extreme caution due
to below normal water levels.

NWSheadline: LOW WATER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 PM EST THIS AFTERNOON... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 6 AM TO 2 PM EST MONDAY
